    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Soldier armed with a halberd, particularly certain civic guards carrying a halberd as a badge of office.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
